description:
Thunderbird 5 picks up an unusual radiation spike from a remote corner of Africa,
and Scott rushes in with Thunderbird 1 to check it out. Using special equipment,
Scott enters the mine and discovers the source to be a leak of unstable uranium.
Moments later he is attacked by a mysterious woman who claims that the mine
belongs to her family. During their confrontation, the mine begins to crumble -
and Scott and she must find a way out.
